类的使用
net.minecraftforge.event.terraingen.BiomeEvent

  • 使用BiomeEvent的程序包 
    程序包 说明
    net.minecraftforge.event.terraingen  

    • net.minecraftforge.event.terraingen中BiomeEvent的使用

      net.minecraftforge.event.terraingen中BiomeEvent的子类 
      修饰符和类型 类 说明
      static class  BiomeEvent.BiomeColor
      BiomeColor is fired whenever an event involving biome colors occurs.
      static class  BiomeEvent.CreateDecorator
      CreateDecorator is fired when a BiomeDecorator is created.
      This event is fired whenever a BiomeDecorator is created in DeferredBiomeDecorator.fireCreateEventAndReplace(Biome).

      BiomeEvent.CreateDecorator.originalBiomeDecorator contains the original BiomeDecorator that would be used in vanilla.
      static class  BiomeEvent.GetFoliageColor
      This event is fired when a biome is queried for its grass color.
      static class  BiomeEvent.GetGrassColor
      This event is fired when a biome is queried for its grass color.
      static class  BiomeEvent.GetVillageBlockID
      This event is fired when the village generator attempts to choose a block ID based on the village's biome.
      static class  BiomeEvent.GetWaterColor
      This event is fired when a biome is queried for its water color.
